summary: 61-year old Chinese woman living in Wuhan City; on 2020-01-05 developed fever, chills, sore throat, headache; 2020-01-08 flight from Wuhan City to Thailand with 5 family members in a 16-people group tour; Fever detected on 2020-01-08 at BKK airport, hospitalized 2020-01-08.
